  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.poster.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.webm?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.mp4?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit distinctive fighters to join your team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your squad into the chaotic battlefield</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire a vast array of extraordinary mods during battles to strengthen your fighters</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Formidable enemies will test your teamwork and strategy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/abbcb5781d179a0cce2734e5e7662a74.webp?t=1751528114\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/abbcb5781d179a0cce2734e5e7662a74.poster.webp?t=1751528114\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=276 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Construction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each playthrough is unique. Whether you succeed or fail, you’ll earn research materials. The logistics and engineering team will make good use of them to bolster your combat capabilities</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d7b1d774da5f27fa9a01bde61fbdec10.poster.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d7b1d774da5f27fa9a01bde61fbdec10.webm?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d7b1d774da5f27fa9a01bde61fbdec10.mp4?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a wide variety of playable characters, each with unique abilities and upgrade paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d83a486ca258aa2789b459847ed15aad.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.poster.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.webm?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/35b4e8944da36d84ca7dca3f06ff6875.mp4?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit distinctive fighters to join your team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your squad into the chaotic battlefield</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire a vast array of extraordinary mods during battles to strengthen your fighters</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Formidable enemies will test your teamwork and strategy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/abbcb5781d179a0cce2734e5e7662a74.webp?t=1751528114\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/abbcb5781d179a0cce2734e5e7662a74.poster.webp?t=1751528114\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=276 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Construction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each playthrough is unique. Whether you succeed or fail, you’ll earn research materials. The logistics and engineering team will make good use of them to bolster your combat capabilities</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d7b1d774da5f27fa9a01bde61fbdec10.poster.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d7b1d774da5f27fa9a01bde61fbdec10.webm?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d7b1d774da5f27fa9a01bde61fbdec10.mp4?t=1751528114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a wide variety of playable characters, each with unique abilities and upgrade paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833540/extras/d83a486ca258aa2789b459847ed15aad.avif?t=1751528114\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p>",
